Class Description
Allied
Allied class represents Allied player.
Artillery
Artillery class represents an artillery as a force which can be moved or can attack.
Axis
Axis class represents Axis player.
Card
Card class represents valid cards for the game.
Cards
Cards class stores the whole cards that is in the game and acts on them.
DiceRoller
DiceRoller class is responsible for rolling the dice.
EnumClasses
EnumClasses class is useless.
Force
Force class represents a force that player can use to attack the enemy.
GameMap
GameMap class implements and presents the map of the game and players.
Infantry
Infantry class represents an individual infantry that can move and attack.
Location
Location class defines a single (row, column) tuple from the map.
Main  
Player
Player class represents a player in the game.
Tank
Tank class represents a tank as a force which can move and attack.
Text
Text class manages all texts and messages which should be printed and some related methods.
